    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based <strong>hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish </strong>with a matching lid, with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p>",
      "order": 2,
