    {
      "instruction": "<p>Score the fatty side of your<strong> pork belly</strong> in a criss-cross pattern by drawing a sharp knife through the skin, deep enough to reach the meat below</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and rub it into the criss-cross pattern</p><p>Add the <strong>scored pork belly</strong>, fat-side down, to the dish and cook for 2 min or until the fat is slightly golden, then remove to a plate</p>",
