    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop your<strong> brown onion[s] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into large chunks</p><p>Top, tail and chop your <strong>carrot[s] </strong>into discs on the diagonal</p><p>Add the <strong>onion wedges </strong>and <strong>carrot discs</strong> to the dish</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1642000691022-x200.jpg",
