          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1642000715583-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pork has had 25 min, reboil the kettle</p><p>Add your<strong> white long grain rice </strong>to<strong> </strong>an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>with 300ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [390ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cover tightly with<strong> tin foil </strong>and put the dish in the oven for 30 min or until all the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
